{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "第八回\"玉绊会不会跑\"讲述了陆小凤追查柳乘风凶案的关键突破。陆小凤将宫萍劫持到偏僻处，通过她身上掉落的玉绊追问其来历。宫萍起初拒绝透露，但两人在斗智斗勇中逐渐建立起信任。宫萍推断出玉绊是男人送给她的，但不肯说出送礼者身份。宫素素现身承认玉绊是她送给宫萍的，却说是柳乘风主动赠送。此时暗器袭击宫萍，陆小凤用她的腰带卷挡暗器，展现出绝顶武功。宫萍最终揭示真相：玉绊实为沙大户转送给宫素素，宫素素为灭口而买凶杀人。陆小凤深夜闯入沙大老板卧室对峙，沙大老板坦承玉绊是他送的，却在追问来源时，沙大老板的妻子突然从被窝跳出，声称玉绊是她丈夫给她的、她有权送人，令陆小凤无功而返。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "宫姑娘，如果你认为我会对你有什么不规矩的行为，那么你就想错了。你一定要相信我，我一向是个非常规矩的人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "如果你真的是个规矩人，为什么要把我绑到这里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "宫姑娘，我第一眼看到你的时候，觉得你实在不怎么样，可是我每多看你一眼，都会觉得你和上次我看你的时候有点不同，看的次数愈多，愈觉得你可爱。我相信，柳先生的看法一定也跟我一样。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "柳先生是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "柳先生现在虽然只不过是个死人而已，可是他活着的时候，却是个很了不起的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他有多了不起？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "至少他绝不会被人迎面一刀刺杀在暗巷中，除非这个人是他很喜欢的人。甚至已经喜欢到可以把他随身佩带的玉绊都送给她。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说的这个'她'，好像是在说一个女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "好像是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说的这个女人，好像就是我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "好像是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说的玉绊，好像就是刚才从我身上掉下来的那一块？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "宫姑娘，不是我恭维你，你实在比我想像中聪明得多。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "陆少爷，不是我不肯恭维你，你实在比我想像中笨得多。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道你说的柳先生就是柳乘风，你一定以为这块玉绊是他送给我的，所以我和他之间的交情当然很密切，所以他才不会提防，所以我才能用我惯用的短刀将他刺杀于暗巷中。你是不是这么想的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就因为你这么想，所以才会把我劫持到这里，所以我才会发觉你是个笨蛋。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "如果我真的杀了柳乘风，我怎么会把他的玉绊放在身上？难道我生怕你不知道我就是杀死你朋友的凶手？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "好，我承认，我是个笨蛋，可是你能不能告诉我，这块玉绊是怎么样会从柳乘风的身上跑到你身上来的呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "又错了。玉绊怎么会跑？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "那么他的玉绊怎么会在你身上？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那当然是有道理的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "什么道理？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "玉绊既然不会跑，我又不会去偷，那么它是从哪里来的？其实你应该明白的，只要你多想一想，一定会明白。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "一个可爱的女人身上，常常都会有一些来历不明的东西，那是为了什么呢？因为有很多男人，虽然又孤寒又小气，要他请朋友吃一顿饭，简直就好像要他的命！可是碰到一个他喜欢的女人，那个女人就算要他的命，他也会给的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "我明白你的意思了。这块玉绊一定是别人送给你的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "男人送女人东西，本来就是天经地义的事情。我肯把他送的东西收下来，他已经高兴得要命了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "对对对！对对对！这个世界上的确有很多男人都是这个样子的。我只不过想知道把这块玉绊送给你的男人是谁？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不会知道他是谁的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我不想告诉你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "我明白你的意思了，你不想告诉我，只因为你不愿意，而且不高兴。对不对？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "天大的理由，也比不上高兴两个字。一个女人要是真的不高兴去做一件事，谁也拿她没法子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "你错了。世上既然有这种不讲理的女人，就有专门对付这种女人的男人。譬如说，我就是这种男人。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你？你能把我怎么样？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "我当然也不能把你怎么样，最多也只不过能把你的裤子脱下来而已。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你用不着吓我，我也不会被你吓住的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不管怎么样，你至少还是个要面子的人，怎么做得出这种事？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "这种事有什么不对？如果你是一个大夫，要看一个病人腿上的伤，你是不是要先把他的裤子脱下来？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "我也一样。如果我不把你的裤子脱下来，怎么能看到你的腿？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是不是大夫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "我不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你既然不是大夫，我的腿也没有受伤，你凭什么要看我的腿？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "刚才我有没有说过一定要大夫才能看别人的腿？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "那么我再问你，我有没有说过一个人一定要等到受了伤之后才能让别人看他的腿？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "所以你现在应该已经明白，一个男人如果要看女人的腿，根本不需要任何理由。幸好我不是那种不讲理的人。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好，那么我问你，你有什么理由？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "因为我一定要找出杀死柳乘风的凶手，只可惜到现在为止我只找到了两条线索，这块玉绊是其中之一，另外一条线索就是一双女人的腿。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "为了这件事，昨天我几乎已经死了一次，死在一个女人的手里。她的脸是易容改扮过的，让人根本看不出她的本来面目，但却在无意中，让我看见了她的腿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你还能认出那双腿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "当然认得出。像那样的腿，男人只要看过一眼就不会忘记，尤其是像我这种有经验的男人。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "你既然不肯告诉我玉绊的来历，我只好看你的腿了。如果我不把你的裤子脱下来，怎么能看到你的腿？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "如果你明白我的意思，那么你就应该知道你的裤子是非脱下来不可的了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是的，我明白你的意思，如果你不是陆小凤，我的裤子恐怕老早已经被脱下来了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "因为，我实在想不到你居然是个这么讲理的女人。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "女人并不是全都不讲理的。只要你说的真有道理，我绝对口服心服。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "那就好极了，真的好极了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "如果你能帮我找出杀死柳乘风的凶手，我永远都会感激你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不想告诉你，我也不能告诉你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "可是你刚刚还说过要帮我忙的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不错，我是说过，而且我一定会做到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "你要怎么做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "照现在这样的情形看，我好像只能让你把我的裤子脱下来。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "陆小凤，我知道你十年前就已名满天下，除了你的轻功和你那两根手指之外，你在女人这一方面的名气也是非常大的。因为每个人都认为你是一个非常了解女人的男人。可是我现在知道，你对女人了解的程度，并不比一个十四岁的小男孩多多少。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道你一定不服气的，身经百战的陆小凤，怎么会不了解女人？可是你真的是不了解，我一点都不骗你，否则你绝不会对我做这种事的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "我对你做过什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我死也不肯的时候，你千方百计的要我相信你一定会脱我的裤子。我相信了，因为我是个很讲理的人，而且觉得你有道理。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以现在我才会心甘情愿的肯让你脱了，你反而好像忘记了这回事。你说，你这是什么意思？你有没有想到过，这对女人来说，是一件多么大的污辱？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "谢谢你。你真可爱，我真的非要谢谢你不可。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你这是什么意思？你为什么要谢谢我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "因为你一直都在鼓励我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我鼓励你？我鼓励你什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "鼓励我把你的腿从你的裤子里面解救出来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "我本来确实不会做这种事的，连你都承认我是个很要面子的人。可是现在你既然一直都在鼓励我，情况当然又不一样了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "一个女人身上，总是难免会有一些来历不明的东西。这些东西当然是男人送的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "男人送女人东西，本来就是天经地义的事，就连你这种男人，有时候都难免会送女人一点东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
      "text": "这块玉绊究竟是怎么来的？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "其实就算你不问，我也应该告诉你，这块玉绊是柳乘风自己送给我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他一到这里，就已经知道我的来历，那一天又恰巧是我的生日，所以他就送了一点礼给我，我也请他喝了一点酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "第一次到我这里来的人，通常都会带一点礼物来送给我的，好像还很少有人例外。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不去追暗算我的人，是因为要保护我，不但怕他们再次出手，而且怕别人伤害我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "别人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "别人当然就是这些年来一直待我很好的宫素素。至少我一直认为她待我很好。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "她怎么会伤害你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道你是故意这么问我的。你知道的应该比我多。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在我甚至怀疑，刚才暗算我的人，也跟她有关系，甚至很可能就是她买来的杀手。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "你认为她有理由要杀你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "有什么理由？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我是惟一知道是谁把这块玉绊送给她的人。所以她要杀我灭口。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "既然她明知这块玉绊很可能成为凶案最重要的线索，她为什么要把它送给你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "第一，那时候她根本想不到有人会不远千里到这里来追查这件凶案，更想不到来的会是你。第二，因为她知道这块玉绊是从死人身上取下的，是件不祥之物，刚巧我看到的时候又很喜欢，所以她就乐得做这个顺水人情。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "从这一点，更可证明她不但知道这块玉绊的来历，而且和刺杀柳乘风的凶手，有非常密切的关系。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这块玉绊当然不是柳乘风自己送给她的，他至死都把这块玉绊带在身上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "那块玉绊是谁送给她的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是沙大户。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "沙大老板",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "滚，不管你是谁，不管你是来干什么的，最好都给我快滚，免得我把你的蛋黄都捏出来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "沙大老板",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "抱歉。我实在真的是抱歉极了，可是我发誓，我绝不是故意来打搅你的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "更抱歉的是，我既不是鸡蛋，也不是鸭蛋，所以也没有什么蛋黄好被你挤出来。我到这里来，只不过想问你一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "我只想问你，你以前有没有看过这样东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "沙大老板",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我当然看见过，而且这还是我送给素云宫主人的节礼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "沙大老板",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "如果你就是为了要问我这件事，就三更半夜的闯到我这里来，那么我告诉你，不管你是谁，你恐怕都很难再完完整整的走出去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "在这种情况下，我只好再问你一件事了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "沙大老板",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "这块玉绊本来是不是你的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "沙大老板",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不是，我常送礼给别人，也常常有人送给我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "沙大老板",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是不是还想问我，这是谁送给我的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "沙大老板",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "如果我不告诉你，你想怎么样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
